        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Starting when you choose this calling at 3rd level, you learn the&nbsp;lightning charge&nbsp;force power, which does not count against your total powers known. Additionally, you can use Wisdom or Charisma as your forcecasting ability for it, and you can use all three Force-Empowered Self options when you cast it as your action and hit the target. Finally, when you deal lightning damage with the&nbsp;lightning charge&nbsp;force power, you deal additional lightning damage equal to half your Wisdom or Charisma modifier (your choice, minimum of one) if it doesn&rsquo;t already include that modifier.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
